Please message us to gain for the copy of full warranty details:  
◆ The items come with one-year warranty. The buyers must contact us to return the defective items for exchange during the warranty.  
◆ The warranty does not extend to any products that are physically damaged or that are not under normal operating conditions as a result of misuse or improper installation on the buyers part.  ◆ We will provide a Returned Merchandise Authorization (RMA) number for each item that needs returning. We do not accept the returns without first requesting a RMA number.  ◆ The items should be returned with our original packaging. 
 ◆ The defective products must be returned within 30 days from the RMA issuing date. Otherwise, no replacement or exchange will be made. The buyers must contact us for the return address for all return products.  
◆ Only partial refund will be completed upon receipt of the returned item if the return is a result of buyers error. We cannot offer the free shipping for the buyers who placed the incorrect order. The buyers are responsible for all the actual shipping cost.  
 ◆ In all cases, the return shipping fees are at buyers own cost to return the items for the exchange or the refund. We are responsible for the postage of the replacements.
